Brenda Fassie is one of South Africa s most loved musicians from the past. Most South Africans would have danced to a Brenda Fassie tune at some point in their life.For some reason this video makes me smile from both the outside and inside.Watch the video of these boere boys dancing to the popular Brenda Fassie song, Vulindlela! Here is the full song Brenda Fassie | Vulindlela